# Prytula Figma вЖТ Component вЖТ Showcase

End-to-end workflow: Figma node вЖТ token mapping (review) вЖТ React component in `web/src/design-system/` вЖТ showcase page in `web/src/showcase/` вЖТ entry in `web/src/showcase/routes.tsx`.

**Always follow `prytula-design-system`** for token names, dedupe rules, and forbidden patterns.

---

## Workflow rule (mandatory)

**Stop after EACH phase and wait for user OK before proceeding.**

| Phase | What happens | STOP вАФ show user |
|-------|----------------|------------------|
| **1** | Read Figma + build token mapping table | Node structure + mapping table. **No code yet.** |
| **2** | Create `design-system/[Name]/` | File list + main `.tsx` (full or clearly labeled excerpt). Suggest `npm run dev` to spot-check in product if wired. |
| **3** | Showcase page + `routes.tsx` | Updated file list + proposed commit message. **Do not commit or push** unless user asks. |

Run one phase only if the user explicitly requests it (e.g. ¬Ђ—В—Ц–ї—М–Ї–Є –Љ–∞–њ—Ц–љ–≥¬ї, ¬Ђ—В—Ц–ї—М–Ї–Є –Ї–Њ–Љ–њ–Њ–љ–µ–љ—В¬ї).

