## Prerequisites

1. **`web/src/styles/tokens.css`** exists (`npm run build:tokens` from repo root).
2. **`web/src/showcase/`** bootstrapped (`ShowcasePage.tsx`, `routes.tsx`, primitives, token pages).
3. Figma MCP available for `get_design_context` / screenshot on the given URL (`node-id` with `-` вЖТ `:` if needed).

## Code layout

| Path | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `web/src/components/` | Product pages (not DS) |
| `web/src/design-system/` | Reusable DS components |
| `web/src/showcase/` | DS docs app at `/showcase/*` |
| `web/src/showcase/routes.tsx` | Nav source of truth |
| `web/src/styles/tokens.css` | Generated CSS variables |

Showcase may import design-system; design-system must **not** import showcase or product.

**Sidebar links:** use absolute paths `to={\`/showcase/${page.path}\`}` вАФ never relative `to={page.path}` (nested routes stack URLs).

